<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Happy Birthday Jannat</title>

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:Arial, sans-serif;
}

body{
    min-height:100vh;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg,#f4f9ff,#e6f2ff);
    padding:20px;
}

.card{
    background:#fff;
    max-width:700px;
    width:100%;
    padding:40px;
    border-radius:20px;
    text-align:center;
    box-shadow:0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
}

h1{
    color:#0d6efd;
    margin-bottom:20px;
}

p{
    color:#444;
    line-height:1.8;
    font-size:18px;
}

button{
    margin-top:25px;
    padding:12px 25px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:10px;
    background:#0d6efd;
    color:white;
    cursor:pointer;
    font-size:16px;
}

button:hover{
    opacity:0.9;
}

#message{
    display:none;
    margin-top:25px;
    padding:20px;
    background:#f8f9fa;
    border-radius:12px;
}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="card">

    <h1>🎂 Happy Birthday, Jannat! 🎂</h1>

    <p>
        Wishing you a wonderful birthday filled with happiness,
        laughter, and beautiful memories.
        May this new year of your life bring success,
        good health, and countless reasons to smile.
    </p>

    <button onclick="showMessage()">Open Birthday Wish 🎁</button>

    <div id="message">

        <h2>🌟 A Special Wish For You 🌟</h2>

        <p>
            May all your dreams come true and may every day
            bring you new opportunities, happiness, and success.
        </p>

        <p>
            Keep smiling, keep shining, and keep being the amazing person you are.
        </p>

        <p>
            🎉 Have a fantastic birthday and an incredible year ahead! 🎉
        </p>

        <p>
            Happy Birthday, Jannat! 🎂✨
        </p>

    </div>

</div>

<script>
function showMessage(){
    document.getElementById("message").style.display="block";
}
</script>

</body>
</html>
